Privacy Policy (English)
→【日本語】
We FANG Inc. comply with laws and guidelines concerning the protection of personal information and provide services according to this privacy policy.
Management of personal information
We will take appropriate safety measures and strictly manage to prevent unauthorized access, loss, damage, falsification, leakage, etc. of your personal information.
Purpose of using personal information
We will acquire the minimum information necessary for each function you use in the application (camera shooting, access to photo album, editing of photo and video data).
In advertisement display, personal information may be used by the following advertisement technology provider.
AdMob (
